{"tid":689482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[瘋傳]先生有野益你 台女子街頭裸拍","createTime":"2018-06-04T06:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T15:29:05.000Z","uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"245cc6f6335f8a2b356d5dbcdeff04c27ce8dac5","tid":689482,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"台灣早前瘋傳一段裸拍影片，一名妙齡女子掀開風衣於台北街頭三點全露，對鏡頭搔首弄姿。台灣警方深入追查後，找到二十四歲的涉事徐姓女子，她解釋影片是被人外流散播，並供稱已因此事得到教訓，苦苦哀求檢警「別讓我家人知道」。<br />\n<br />\n　　該條長三十五秒的短片近日在網上廣傳，片中徐女身穿風衣，在台北民生社區附近遊蕩，期間更有多輛車子及多名路人經過；但走到暗處，她突然打開風衣裸露三點，拍攝的姓錢男友更伸手觸摸其胸部。警方其後以妨害風化、散佈猥褻物品等罪名控告二人，但檢方調查後認為，徐女雖涉犯公然猥褻罪，但事後坦承犯行、深具悔意，決定不作起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/chi/673511/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fchi%2F673511%2F&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=39c5502e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fchi%2F673511%2F&h=77a9ba4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/chi/673511/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/03/16/1284346-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F1284346-XXL.jpg&h=002a1ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fc486f3709f8a812c921411550474367308536","tid":689482,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb1d58866d7f99ca762722409f27ae1ac4da2ce","tid":689482,"uid":61169,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"r